videos.description: Albany's Marvin Branch makes a diving interception to give the Great Danes great field position.
videos.headline: Albany defense making an INT look easy

videos.description: ODU's Ray Lawry finds a hole and takes it to the house to put the Monarchs up 7-0.
videos.headline: Monarchs strike first with 41-yard rushing TD

videos.description: Monarchs' Brandon Simmons punches it in from 2 yards away to add to ODU's lead.
videos.headline: Old Dominion goes right up the middle for another rushing TD

videos.description: Monarchs' Gemonta Jackson is the third RB to score on a rushing TD tonight making it 21-3.
videos.headline: ODU spreading the wealth on their third rushing TD

videos.description: QB Will Brunson converts on 2nd and 18 with the longest play from scrimmage for Albany.
videos.headline: Albany QB Will Brunson finds running room to move the chains

videos.description: QB Neven Sussman keeps it up the middle for a 3 yard rushing TD to cut the Monarch's lead.
videos.headline: Albany scores their first TD of the 2017 campaign

videos.description: ODU QB Blake LaRussa tosses it up in coverage and the Great Danes' Kareem Brown comes down with the INT.
videos.headline: Albany gathers their second INT of the night

videos.description: RB Karl Mofor splits the defense and scores from 69 yards bringing the Great Danes to within a TD
videos.headline: Don't sleep on Albany! A long rushing TD puts them within 7
